{"word":"κλίνη","slug":"κλίνη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κλίνη</b></el> <el>(κλί¯νη, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλίνω'><el>κλίνω</el></a>\n<p/><i>that on which one lies, a couch</i> or <i>bed</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—also, <i>a bier</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}